From: Balasubramanian Narasimhan <b.naras@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 8 Mar 2026 15:09:35 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] CRAN compliance: disable fmt string_view, redirect I/O to
 R

- Disable FMT_USE_STRING_VIEW to avoid deprecated char_traits<signed char>
  on libc++ (LLVM 18+)
- Replace std::cerr/std::cout with r_cerr()/r_cout() for R compatibility
